Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是来探病的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是不想待在办公室里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次见到红老师可别再晕倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就别提这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次 看鸣人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她完全晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着浑身是伤的鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手婆婆 我有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 和鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像脸色非常红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连赤丸也嫉妒的超追踪力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找梦幻的微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是纲手大人亲自审问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木还是什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能够找到大蛇丸的线索已经完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他也是大蛇丸的弃子之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不知道佐助的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和水木拼命战斗 结果却是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人无法接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说纲手婆婆 没关系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不行就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人现在也无法专心工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人一直都缠着她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能批准他去找佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就偷偷溜出了办公室…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果中了埋伏 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说好几遍了 让我去找佐助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也说好几遍了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要修炼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人不在 修炼不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸也好 佐助也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有他们的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有办法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有消息的话 我会去打听的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个不明事理的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手婆婆也是个不明事理的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 不错 宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里要再往前半步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧 宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也喝点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田既然来了 也该多看会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是看看 也是一种修炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开饭了 开饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经接近完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了两位的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天陪我来这里特训
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一个小队的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队里的同伴有困难的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们当然会出手帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是理所当然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有一个同伴突然失踪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定非常痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说鸣人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能帮帮他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然想帮他做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人也对鸣人说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有线索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办法倒是有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被称为梦幻之虫的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说很早以前就已经绝种了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为怕他绝种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们油女一族也停止使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 应该还有少数存活在某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人 那个微香虫是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次使用微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也距离上次大战很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香虫是虫使所用虫的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从卵里出生的幼虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一会儿就成了蛹 然后化羽成虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让它们去辨认气味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使很微弱也能找到这股味道的来源
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的嗅觉是忍犬的几千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着超强的寻人能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过微香虫好像几年才产一次卵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年正好是产卵之年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在正好也是孵化的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子里还有佐助留下的东西 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让微香虫闻这个气味的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能知道佐助的所在地了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够找到微香虫的概率是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说并不高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计有10%的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在村子正处于非常困难的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是下忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能随便地自由行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞翁失马焉知非福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为红进了医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也基本没任务可执行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其闲着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如去赌一赌这10%的概率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油女志乃 犬冢牙 日向雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在命令你们去寻找微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次由志乃指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 那边的老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不让你去也不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来只有让你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这可是最后的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找不到微香虫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对佐助的事死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 一定会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 可别食言哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个得意忘形的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宁次马上就要过来修炼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶点就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下要去执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别拖大家的后腿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个大转身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么走这么慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以忍者的速度走到微香虫的栖息地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要两天左右的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要一开始就这么着急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在我们到之前卵就孵化了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香虫的卵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雨后的第二天早晨才会孵化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时还不会下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 可是 万一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本队的队长是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务中请听队长的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难想象你至今是怎么和那个家伙相处的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:12:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会和鸣人成为好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人他们刚才出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找虫子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃最合适不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有拥有白眼的雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及嗅觉超群的牙和赤丸同行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没必要再去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下我的任务就是尽快成为医疗忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天快黑了 搭帐篷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经搭帐篷了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点儿都不累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往前走点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 本队的队长是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经睡觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多数动植物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日落则眠 日出则醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要寻找虫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须亲身去体会它们的生活节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 太阳才刚落山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 本队的队长是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早怎么可能睡得着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说 竟然这么快就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 吓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了这么久 还没睡够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上起来小便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到一件不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田也感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么个不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布里有个非常漂亮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人挥手的同时 水也舞动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上去打招呼时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是做梦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏田的脸非常红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会真感冒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个果实可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就吃它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也能节约我们的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一点要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一种人型大的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了会狂泻不止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要碰它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有哪个傻瓜会吃那么大的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 要出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马…上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是第一次看到这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像人能生活的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以对虫子们来说就是乐园了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个比中忍考试简单多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 太脆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为队长我有一个警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候 什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不说我也知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要警告你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成之后 一定要好好揍你一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是微香虫之森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是木叶的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里的话 说明他们的目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 和我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝不会把微香虫让给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香虫是我们上水流一族的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个照片的虫子我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 没想到这就是微香虫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上在厨房里偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是便用拖鞋…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:22:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的只不过是普通的蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:22:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不对了 虫子怎么看都一样